The '''United States Senate election of 1882''' was an election which had the [[Republican Party (United States)| Republican Party]] obtain an outright majority in the [[United States Senate]].

As this election was prior to ratification of the [[Seventeenth Amendment to the United States Constitution|seventeenth amendment]], Senators were chosen by [[State legislature (United States)|State legislatures]].

== Results ==
[[48th United States Congress|48th Congress]] (1883â1885) 

* Majority Party: Republican (38)
* Minority Party: Democratic (36)
* Other Parties: [[Readjuster Party|Readjuster]] (2)
* '''Total Seats: 76'''

